            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "There’s no doubt the new Ford Bronco is hot property these days, thanks to strong demand coupled with weak supply thanks in part to the chip shortage. However, this Bronco someone made out of snow is, well, ice cold. A talented snow sculpture artist named Eric Jones posted a photo of his handiwork to Facebook and it is definitely impressive.",
